    <h5 {...{
      "id": "region-1"
    }}>{`Region`}</h5>
    <p>{`The region parameter contains n values. Each value represents a coordinate (x,y) and are seperated by the "|" delimiter. These coordinates are used to calculate the concave hull. Pixels of interest that lie within the concave hull are valid pixels; if not they are invalid.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
