    <h3 {...{
      "id": "sequence"
    }}>{`Sequence`}</h3>
    <p>{`This is a trivial heuristic. The sequence heuristic will store a single integer in memory, that will count the numbers of valid detections. When the heuristic will detect a false detection, it will decrease the count. The sequence heuristic will return true, if a threshold is reached; for example when something was detected three times in a row.`}</p>
