    <h5 {...{
      "id": "minimum-changes"
    }}>{`Minimum changes`}</h5>
    <p>{`The heuristic will only return true if enough changes have been detected. The minimum of changes indicates the minimum number of pixels that have to been changed, to be a valid detection.`}</p>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "minimum-durations"
    }}>{`Minimum durations`}</h5>
    <p>{`The minimum number of detections in a row to be a valid detection.`}</p>
    <h5 {...{
      "id": "no-motion-delay-time"
    }}>{`No motion delay time`}</h5>
    <p>{`When the heuristic failed, due to not enough pixels changed or not x detections in a row, the heuristic will idle for some time.`}</p>
