    <h3 {...{
      "id": "mqtt"
    }}>{`MQTT`}</h3>
    <p>{`MQTT protocol is a light-weight Machine to Machine (M2M) protocol widely used in Internet of things.
Detailed information (a JSON object) is published to an MQTT topic. The JSON object contains the number of changes, the region, the URL of the image, etc.`}</p>
