    <h5 {...{
      "id": "example-1"
    }}>{`Example`}</h5>
    <p>{`It is possible to subscribe multiple distributed IoT devices to the same MQTT topic and perform specific actions upon the detection of a motion. Devices with more resources could fetch the image to perform further elaboration.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "streaming"
